rong>LASIK</strong>\r\n\r\nConta com uma alta taxa de experiência e é amplamente disponível.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>PRK</strong>\r\n\r\nO processo de recuperação pode levar um período maior que as demais.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','CIRURGIAS REFRATIVAS: ENTENDA AS DIFERENÇAS','Consulte o médico para saber qual a mais adequada para o seu caso.','inherit','closed','closed','','54-revision-v1','','','2018-06-27 01:14:06','2018-06-27 04:14:06','',54,'http://cirurgiasmile.com.br/blog/2018/06/27/54-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(57,1,'2018-06-27 01:19:14','2018-06-27 04:19:14','','logo-central','','inherit','open','closed','','logo-central','','','2018-06-27 01:19:14','2018-06-27 04:19:14','',0,'http://cirurgiasmile.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/logo-central.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(58,1,'2018-06-27 01:19:19','2018-06-27 04:19:19','','texto-rodape','','inherit','open','closed','','texto-rodape-2','','','2018-06-27 01:19:19','2018-06-27 04:19:19','',0,'http://cirurgiasmile.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/texto-rodape-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(59,1,'2018-06-27 01:19:52','2018-06-27 04:19:52','[pexcontentslider pex_attr_sliderid=\"9\"][/pexcontentslider]\r\n\r\n[sc name=\"sobre\"]\r\n\r\n[pexblogposts pex_attr_cat=\"8\" pex_attr_layout=\"columns\" pex_attr_number=\"3\" pex_attr_columns=\"3\"][/pexblogposts]\r\n<div id=\"smile-no-mundo\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-8 size-full\" src=\"http://cirurgiasmile.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/infografico-2.jpg\" alt=\"smile no mundo presente em 65 países 1300 cirurgiões 1 milhão de olhos tratados\" width=\"1919\" height=\"498\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"lista-clinicas\"></div>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-revision-v1','','','2018-06-27 01:19:52','2018-06-27 04:19:52','',4,'http://cirurgiasmile.com.br/blog/2018/06/27/4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(60,1,'2018-06-27 01:33:16','2018-06-27 04:33:16','[pexcontentslider pex_attr_sliderid=\"9\"][/pexcontentslider]\r\n\r\n[sc name=\"sobre\"]